Full loop in motion

Here’s the complete runtime:

User compares two Pokémon
→ BLP binds the entities and action
→ CE converts comparisons into a preference graph
→ CMP packages that graph into valuable outputs
→ UICL assigns credit to the user and other contributors
→ output gets reused
→ reuse generates more value
→ more value flows back into the ledger

That is the full machine.

